headline: How the Narrative Surrounding Chipotle Has Shifted Amid Traffic Headwinds and Lowered Price Targets
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill's stock narrative is shifting as analysts recalibrate their outlook, leaving the Fair Value Estimate steady at about $43.18 per share even as the discount rate inches higher and revenue growth assumptions ease slightly. The Street now largely clusters around price targets in the mid $40s, reflecting both confidence in the long term brand story and caution around near term traffic and comp trends.
